extensions.description: Saving one dolphin won’t change the world, but it will change the world for that one dolphin
Support for GRIGORY, food for GRIGORY, for GRIGORY creativity. POOON

Legend has it that the first Dog Bundled appeared when dozens of meme dogs — Doge, Cheems, Shiba, Walter, Gabe, and others — gathered to protect the internet from boring tokens. They united into a single digital package, and thus DB was born.
